title: As Told by Ginger, Season 1 (SD iTunes WEB-DL)
description:
Well, here we go again.
Since the old DLs of this show are from VHS tapes (or something like that), you got something for the new year.

The complete Season 1 of As Told by Ginger, ripped from iTunes.

Since the show on the iTS is divided by "Volumes", this includes Vol. 1 and 2.

English audio, English CC track, all the iTunes metadata.

And as some people from certain robotics company say: Share and enjoy!

(I only have 15Mb UL speed here, so keep this alive. I'll upload season 2 as soon as I finish downloading it and decrypting it.)
